Package nl.naturalis.geneious.note

Class NaturalisNote

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.naturalis.geneious.note.NaturalisNote
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Note
    public final class NaturalisNote
extends Object
implements Note
    A container for all annotations that can be added using the Naturalis plugin. A NaturalisNote will never contain null or whitespace-only values. This even applies to non-string fields: calling toString() on them must never return null or a whitespace-only string. Trying to set any field to null or to a whitespace-only string results in an IllegalArgumentException. Consequently, if a NaturalisNote extracted from a Geneious document returns null for a particular field, it means the field was not present in the Geneious document.
    Author:
    Ayco Holleman
